      "comment": "BLAME HER (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 27.65 beating STAR ZITTO. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. FORMULA FUN (5) turned in a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 488m behind BLAME HER (28.24) in a Grade 4/5. Likely to be about the money. MILITARIES (1) resumed in a Grade 4/5 at this track and finished seventh over 488m (28.57). Solid record here winning four races. Boasts two wins from three starts out of this box. Can figure in the finish. JAFFA'S MONELLI (3) collected a minor prize last start and ran time in the process - must be considered.",
